# imhof-sia-upsurging


This is a pyhon implementation of the UPSURGING scheme that inhibits negative ice thickness in shallow ice approximation ice flow models based on finite differences. 

Fore more details see the dissertation of Michael Andreas Imhof, "Combined climate-ice flow modelling of the Alpine Ice Field during the Last Glacial Maximum", 2021, ETH Zurich, dissertation no. 27416, DOI:???





